#### Brings you:

# Kerbal Inventory System No Fun (QBKN)
Module Manager Script for removing "fun" items from Kerbal Inventory System.

Available on CKAN as `KerbalInventorySystemNoFun`.

Requires [Kerbal Inventory System][thread:kis]. (CKAN:KIS)  

#### Adopted by [@zer0Kerbal][LINK:zer0kerbal], originally by [@QuickBASIC][LINK:QuickBASIC]
